-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Arrays
/+/ Similar to lists, to define an array 
/+/ Arrays are not objects
/+/ 
int[] array1 = new int[3]; //new int [3] says that this array is size 3.
array1[0] = 10;
array1[1] = 20;
array1[2] = 30;
// these three statments set the three slots in the array to 10, 20, and 30. 
/+/ Methods for arrays include:
.length //do not use() 

